a\";s:31:\"Mon, 22 Aug 2016 09:23:07 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Compatibility\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://wpml.org/?p=1002746\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:371:\"Introduction Meta Slider is an easy-to-use WordPress slider plugin. Its integration with WPML allows you to translate your sliders. In this tutorial, we will provide you with detailed instructions on how to translate your sliders. Required Plugins Meta Slider plugin (version 2.1.31 or above) A recent version of WPML (version 3.3.7 or above) String Translation [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Mohamed Khafaja\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14930:\"<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1003198 size-full\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Meta-Slider-and-WPML.png\" alt=\"Meta Slider and WPML\" width=\"680\" height=\"109\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Meta-Slider-and-WPML.png 680w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Meta-Slider-and-WPML-150x24.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Meta-Slider-and-WPML-300x48.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" /></p>\n<h2>Introduction</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/ml-slider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Meta Slider</a> is an easy-to-use WordPress slider plugin. Its integration with WPML allows you to translate your sliders. In this tutorial, we will provide you with detailed instructions on how to translate your sliders.</p>\n<h2>Required Plugins</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/ml-slider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Meta Slider</a> plugin (version 2.1.31 or above)</li>\n<li>A recent version of <a href=\"https://wpml.org/purchase/\">WPML</a> (version 3.3.7 or above) String Translation and the Media Translation add-on</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Essential Resources</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>WPML‚Äôs <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/getting-started-guide/\">Getting Started Guide</a>¬†helps you in setting up WPML in a few minutes. You will want to refer later to some of its subtopics, such as <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/getting-started-guide/media-translation/\">Media Translation</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.metaslider.com/documentation/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Meta Slider documentation</a> provides step-by-step instructions on how to create, customize, and insert sliders into pages.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Getting started</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Install and activate the WPML plugin along with the Media translation add-on.</li>\n<li>Install and activate the Meta Slider Gallery plugin.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Content</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Create your default language slider.</li>\n<li>Create your secondary language slider.</li>\n<li>Insert the default language slider into the page/post and translate it.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Create your default language slider</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Make sure that your admin bar language switcher is set to your default language.</li>\n<li>Click on the <strong>Meta Slider</strong> menu item on your WordPress dashboard.</li>\n<li>Click on the ‚Äú<strong>+</strong>‚Äù icon to add a new slider.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Creat-default-language-slider-1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1002909\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Creat-default-language-slider-1-300x178.png\" alt=\"Creat default language slider\" width=\"550\" height=\"326\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Creat-default-language-slider-1-300x178.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Creat-default-language-slider-1-150x89.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Creat-default-language-slider-1-768x456.png 768w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Creat-default-language-slider-1.png 907w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>Click on the <strong>Add Slide </strong>button to add your images (slides). This allows you to add images from your media library or even upload new ones, then click on the <strong>Add to slider </strong>button.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Add-slides-1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1003132\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Add-slides-1-300x135.png\" alt=\"Add slides\" width=\"550\" height=\"248\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Add-slides-1-300x135.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Add-slides-1-150x68.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Add-slides-1-768x346.png 768w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Add-slides-1-1024x461.png 1024w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Add-slides-1.png 1311w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>Add the title for your slider.</li>\n<li>Add the slide (image) meta-data (caption, title, and Alt text<strong>)</strong></li>\n<li>Click on the <strong>Save¬†</strong>button.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Add-slider-translated-title-and-slides-meta-data-1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1003097\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Add-slider-translated-title-and-slides-meta-data-1-300x109.png\" alt=\"Add slider translated title and slides meta-data\" width=\"550\" height=\"199\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Add-slider-translated-title-and-slides-meta-data-1-300x109.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Add-slider-translated-title-and-slides-meta-data-1-150x54.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Add-slider-translated-title-and-slides-meta-data-1-768x278.png 768w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Add-slider-translated-title-and-slides-meta-data-1-1024x371.png 1024w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Add-slider-translated-title-and-slides-meta-data-1.png 1187w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<ol start=\"8\">\n<li>Copy the slider‚Äôs short-code¬† as we will need to paste it into the default language page/post a bit later.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Defualt-language-slider-short-code-1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1003121\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Defualt-language-slider-short-code-1.png\" alt=\"Defualt language slider short code\" width=\"450\" height=\"282\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Defualt-language-slider-short-code-1.png 271w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Defualt-language-slider-short-code-1-150x94.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Note: if¬†you had images in your media library before installing WPML. On your WordPress dashboard navigate to WPML -&gt; Media Translation -&gt; Make sure that all the options as shown below in the <strong>existing media</strong> section -&gt; Click on the <strong>Start</strong> button. Read more about the <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/getting-started-guide/media-translation/\">Media Translation Module</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Handeling-media-translation-1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1010831\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Handeling-media-translation-1.png\" alt=\"Handeling media translation\" width=\"550\" height=\"355\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Handeling-media-translation-1.png 896w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Handeling-media-translation-1-150x97.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Handeling-media-translation-1-300x194.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Handeling-media-translation-1-768x496.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<h2>Create your secondary language slider</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Use the admin bar language switcher found on your WordPress dashboard to switch to your secondary language.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Switch-to-secondary-language.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1002984\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Switch-to-secondary-language-300x80.png\" alt=\"Switch to secondary language\" width=\"550\" height=\"146\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Switch-to-secondary-language-300x80.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Switch-to-secondary-language-150x40.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Switch-to-secondary-language.png 482w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Click on the ‚Äú<strong>+</strong>‚Äù icon to create your secondary language slider.</li>\n<li>Follow the same steps to add the slides (images) to your slider.</li>\n<li>Add the translated title for your slider.</li>\n<li>Add the slide (image) translated meta-data texts (caption, title and Alt text<strong>)</strong></li>\n<li>Click on the <strong>Save </strong>button and copy the slider‚Äôs short-code to be added later to the translated page.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Add-slider-translated-title-and-slides-meta-data-3.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1003157\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Add-slider-translated-title-and-slides-meta-data-3-300x109.png\" alt=\"Add slider translated title and slides meta-data\" width=\"550\" height=\"199\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Add-slider-translated-title-and-slides-meta-data-3-300x109.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Add-slider-translated-title-and-slides-meta-data-3-150x54.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Add-slider-translated-title-and-slides-meta-data-3-768x278.png 768w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Add-slider-translated-title-and-slides-meta-data-3-1024x371.png 1024w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Add-slider-translated-title-and-slides-meta-data-3.png 1187w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<h2>Insert the default language slider into the page/post and translate it</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>On your WordPress dashboard click on <strong>Pages</strong> -&gt; <strong>Add New</strong> to create a new page and insert the slider to it, or you can choose one of your existing pages.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Please make sure to choose your default language from the admin bar language switcher.</p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Add the title and page content and paste the slider short-code of the default language slider.</li>\n<li>Click on the <strong>Publish </strong>button.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/English-slider-page.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1003009\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/English-slider-page-300x148.png\" alt=\"English slider page\" width=\"550\" height=\"271\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/English-slider-page-300x148.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/English-slider-page-150x74.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/English-slider-page-768x378.png 768w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/English-slider-page-1024x504.png 1024w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/English-slider-page.png 1204w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>Click on the ‚Äú<strong>+</strong>‚Äù icon found on the language meta-box on the right to add the translated text to your page.</li>\n<li>Paste the secondary language short-code for your slider and click on the <strong>Publish </strong>button.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/French-slider-page.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1003021\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/French-slider-page-300x151.png\" alt=\"French slider page\" width=\"550\" height=\"276\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/French-slider-page-300x151.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/French-slider-page-150x75.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/French-slider-page-768x385.png 768w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/French-slider-page-1024x514.png 1024w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/French-slider-page.png 1192w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Note that you can use the <strong>Add Slider </strong>button to insert the slider into the page/post.</p>\n<p>This is how the sliders look on the front-end:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Front-end-in-English.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1003059\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Front-end-in-English-300x106.png\" alt=\"Front end in English\" width=\"550\" height=\"194\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Front-end-in-English-300x106.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Front-end-in-English-150x53.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Front-end-in-English-768x271.png 768w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Front-end-in-English-1024x362.png 1024w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Front-end-in-English.png 1109w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Front-end-in-French.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1003070\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Front-end-in-French-300x107.png\" alt=\"Front end in French\" width=\"550\" height=\"195\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Front-end-in-French-300x107.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Front-end-in-French-150x53.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Front-end-in-French-768x273.png 768w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Front-end-in-French-1024x364.png 1024w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Front-end-in-French.png 1103w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<h2>Conclusion</h2>\n<p>If you are running a multilingual website it is important to translate all of its elements. Meta Slider is fully compatible with WPML, which allows you to translate your sliders effortlessly. In this tutorial, we have created two instances of the slider. The first one is inserted to our default language page and the other is inserted in our secondary language page.</p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=7q_Ibp5U8g4:BSwePN9gbaU:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=7q_Ibp5U8g4:BSwePN9gbaU:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=7q_Ibp5U8g4:BSwePN9gbaU:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=7q_Ibp5U8g4:BSwePN9gbaU:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=7q_Ibp5U8g4:BSwePN9gbaU:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=7q_Ibp5U8g4:BSwePN9gbaU:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/7q_Ibp5U8g4\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"https://wpml.org/2016/08/translate-meta-slider-plugin-using-wpml/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://wpml.org/2016/08/translate-meta-slider-plugin-using-wpml/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:45:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:46:\"Compatible WooCommerce Extensions ‚Äì Aug 2016\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/wpml/~3/4XcXbQ5Sf_I/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"https://wpml.org/2016/08/compatible-woocommerce-extensions-aug-2016/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 16 Aug 2016 10:06:45 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Compatibility\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://wpml.org/?p=1004521\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:377:\"Today we are happy to announce a couple of compatible WooCommerce Extensions. The Extensions¬†are, Woocommerce Color or Image Variation Swatches, Woocommerce Wholesale Ordering If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here: Multilingual Ready Themes Multilingual Ready Plugins Also, if you‚Äôre a theme [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Mohamed Khafaja\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3933:\"<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-910927\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Compatible-woocommerce-extention-header-image-300x84.png\" alt=\"Compatible woocommerce extention header image\" width=\"400\" height=\"112\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Compatible-woocommerce-extention-header-image-300x84.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Compatible-woocommerce-extention-header-image-150x42.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Compatible-woocommerce-extention-header-image.png 568w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></p>\n<p>Today we are happy to announce a couple of compatible WooCommerce Extensions.</p>\n<p>The Extensions¬†are, <a href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/woocommerce-color-or-image-variation-swatches/7444039\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Woocommerce Color or Image Variation Swatches</a>, <a href=\"https://stephensherrardplugins.com/plugins/woocommerce-wholesale-ordering/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Woocommerce Wholesale Ordering</a></p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you‚Äôre a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process, we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our¬†<a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Woocommerce Color or Image Variation Swatches</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Convert your normal variable attribute dropdown select to nicely looking color or image select. You can display images or color in all common size. Display them in round or square mode.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/woocommerce-color-or-image-variation-swatches/7444039\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Woocommerce Color or Image Variation Swatches</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Woocommerce Wholesale Ordering</h2>\n<blockquote><p>With Woocommerce Wholesale Ordering you can create Wholesale Customer user accounts that allow those users to see and order at wholesale prices. Easily filter orders in the admin dashboard by Wholesale or Retail orders.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://stephensherrardplugins.com/plugins/woocommerce-wholesale-ordering/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Woocommerce Wholesale Ordering</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=4XcXbQ5Sf_I:fI85DVttRRM:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=4XcXbQ5Sf_I:fI85DVttRRM:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=4XcXbQ5Sf_I:fI85DVttRRM:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=4XcXbQ5Sf_I:fI85DVttRRM:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=4XcXbQ5Sf_I:fI85DVttRRM:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=4XcXbQ5Sf_I:fI85DVttRRM:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/4XcXbQ5Sf_I\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"https://wpml.org/2016/08/compatible-woocommerce-extensions-aug-2016/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"https://wpml.org/2016/08/compatible-woocommerce-extensions-aug-2016/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"WPML 3.5 released, with major improvements to String Translation\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/wpml/~3/oJhBQIMBYWk/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:98:\"https://wpml.org/2016/08/wpml-3-5-released-with-major-improvements-to-string-translation/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 15 Aug 2016 19:48:03 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"WPML versions\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://wpml.org/?p=1003642\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:378:\"After months of development, we&#8217;ve just released WPML 3.5. This version focuses on String Translation, improving performance and adding few features. WPML 3.5 also handles a few compatibility issues with WordPress 4.6. Compatible with WordPress 4.6 WordPress 4.6 is almost ready (due tomorrow morning). This update of WPML includes a number of changes to support [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Amir\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9064:\"<p><strong>After months of development, we&#8217;ve just released <a href=\"https://wpml.org/version/wpml-3-5-0/\">WPML 3.5</a>. This version focuses on String Translation, improving performance and adding few features. WPML 3.5 also handles a few compatibility issues with WordPress 4.6.</strong></p>\n<h2>Compatible with WordPress 4.6</h2>\n<p>WordPress 4.6 is almost ready (due tomorrow morning). This update of WPML includes a number of changes to support WordPress 4.6. Before you upgrade WordPress, be sure to upgrade WPML and all its add-ons. Like we recommend in every WordPress release, you should update with caution. We always test first on a staging site, review the site and see that nothing is broken, check the PHP error log and see that it&#8217;s clean and then update. Before updating the production site (even after we&#8217;ve tested on a staging site), we prepare a complete backup.</p>\n<p>Usually, we never need to use that backup. However, in the very rare cases when it&#8217;s needed, having this backup will prove to be a good idea.</p>\n<h2>String Translation improvements</h2>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1003739\" style=\"width: 310px\" class=\"wp-caption alignright\"><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/wpml35-load.png\"><img src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/wpml35-load-300x166.png\" alt=\"Average load changes for String Translation, between WPML 3.4 and WPML 3.5\" width=\"300\" height=\"166\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-1003739\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/wpml35-load-300x166.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/wpml35-load-150x83.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/wpml35-load.png 665w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Average load changes for String Translation, between WPML 3.4 and WPML 3.5</p></div>We introduced the changes to String Translation in the <a href=\"https://wpml.org/2016/08/wpml-3-5-beta1-announcement/\">WPML 3.5 beta announcement blog post</a>. Since the betas, we&#8217;ve made more performance improvements to String Translation in the admin and front-end. The overall performance improvement numbers depend on your content, the theme, other plugins and PHP version.</p>\n<p>The graph on the right looks very promising, but please keep in mind WHAT we&#8217;re showing there. These are the numbers for String Translation only. Of course, a real site has more running than WPML String Translation. On our production site, the overall improvement is about 5% in CPU and 10% in memory. From that, you can see the part that String Translation was responsible for. We&#8217;re also running PHP 7.</p>\n<p>Generally speaking, sites that have a large number of strings, not so many other plugins and run PHP 5.x will see the greatest performance improvement. PHP 7 is already a lot faster than PHP 5, especially for the functions that String Translation uses. There&#8217;s a significant performance improvement with PHP 7, but it&#8217;s smaller than on PHP 5 (which is a good thing). Sites that have many many plugins are likely to be less optimized for performance, so the overall gain from the new String Translation is less significant.</p>\n<p>Since the performance gain in WPML 3.5 is both in CPU and in memory allocation, it&#8217;s best to measure the actual server load, rather than only use a profiling plugin. Profiling plugins are great, but they don&#8217;t give you the full picture of how your site handles real load.</p>\n<p>I recommend to check:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The overall server load, both CPU and memory</li>\n<li>The response time for front-end pages</li>\n<li>The response time for admin pages</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We will be monitoring the server loads of our sites and will post updates about the changes that we&#8217;re seeing. We need a week to collect these updated stats, so that we can show a meaningful comparison.</p>\n<h3>A bit more coming in WPML 3.5.1</h3>\n<p>The last pocket of inefficiency is in the interaction between GetText and WPML. Today, translation happens twice. WordPress loads .mo files, which sometimes are huge. Then, WPML basically overrides all translations in String Translation.</p>\n<p>You can see how this is wasting resources.</p>\n<p>In WPML 3.5.1, we are planning to prevent WordPress from loading .mo files for contexts that String Translation is handling. You will not lose anything and only gain in page load time. This gain can be very significant, because WPML now only loads the strings that are needed for each page (while WordPress would load the entire .mo file).</p>\n<p>WordPress 4.6 changed the loading of .mo files. Now that it&#8217;s out, we can complete this feature in WPML.</p>\n<h3>A glitch in String Translation update causes a (harmless) warning</h3>\n<p>Immediately after release of WPML 3.5, we noticed a <a href=\"https://wpml.org/errata/possible-db-errors-upgrading-string-translation-2-4-0/\">cosmetic glitch which may happen in some of the sites updating automatically</a>. These messages will appear only once and they don&#8217;t cause any problem to the site.</p>\n<p>This glitch doesn&#8217;t look nice, but it&#8217;s not causing any damage. Since WPML 3.5 is needed for WordPress 4.6 (which is coming out tomorrow), we didn&#8217;t hold with that update. We&#8217;ll fix that glitch tomorrow morning and release a minor update for WPML String Translation.</p>\n<h2>Removed the WPML Widget from the WordPress Dashboard</h2>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1003719\" style=\"width: 310px\" class=\"wp-caption alignright\"><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/removed-wpml-widget-1.png\"><img src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/removed-wpml-widget-1-300x243.png\" alt=\"How many widgets with &quot;useful information&quot; appear on your Admin Dashboard? Could they be slowing down sites?\" width=\"300\" height=\"243\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-1003719\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/removed-wpml-widget-1-300x243.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/removed-wpml-widget-1-150x122.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/removed-wpml-widget-1-768x623.png 768w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/removed-wpml-widget-1-1024x830.png 1024w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/removed-wpml-widget-1.png 1167w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">How many widgets with &#8220;useful information&#8221; appear on your Admin Dashboard? Could they be slowing down sites?</p></div>Until WPML 3.5 there was a WPML Widget on the Admin Dashboard. This widget started with good intentions, but grew to be a resource sink. Over time, we kept adding all sorts of information to that widget. It pulled and displayed recent blog posts, the languages summary and translation status and a host of other trivia. You can imagine that all this wonderfully useless information required database queries (and some remote queries) and PHP processing.</p>\n<p>We decided that the added value in this information doesn&#8217;t justify the load it produces and we removed it. If you feel that any of that information was useful to you, let us know. Our admin dashboard became a lot faster, just by removing that widget.</p>\n<p>As a side note, while reviewing that widget, we noticed a few similar widgets, suggestions and &#8220;nice to know&#8221; tips from other plugins and themes. If you&#8217;re seeing them on your dashboard, make sure that they&#8217;re not slowing down your sites (like WPML&#8217;s widget did).</p>\n<h2>Download and update</h2>\n<p>As always, the best way to get updates to WPML is by registering your sites and updating automatically. You can always download from your <a href=\"https://wpml.org/account/\">WPML account</a>. Be sure to update all of WPML&#8217;s components that you&#8217;re using.</p>\n<h2>Feedback?</h2>\n<p>Let us know your thoughts about this update by leaving a comment. We&#8217;re eager to know how it&#8217;s working for you. If you need help resolving problems, please first create a ticket in our <a href=\"https://wpml.org/forums/forum/english-support/\">technical support forum</a>. Then, add a comment here with a brief description and a link to the support ticket.</p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=oJhBQIMBYWk:RjuV_sLVfLY:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=oJhBQIMBYWk:RjuV_sLVfLY:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=oJhBQIMBYWk:RjuV_sLVfLY:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=oJhBQIMBYWk:RjuV_sLVfLY:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=oJhBQIMBYWk:RjuV_sLVfLY:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=oJhBQIMBYWk:RjuV_sLVfLY:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/oJhBQIMBYWk\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:94:\"https://wpml.org/2016/08/wpml-3-5-released-with-major-improvements-to-string-translation/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"13\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:89:\"https://wpml.org/2016/08/wpml-3-5-released-with-major-improvements-to-string-translation/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"Known issues related to shipping costs in WooCommerce Multilingual 3.8.4\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/wpml/~3/6gzGAI20aL0/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:99:\"https://wpml.org/2016/08/known-issues-related-shipping-cost-woocommerce-multilingual-3-8-4/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 10 Aug 2016 09:04:52 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"https://wpml.org/?p=997310\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:360:\"WooCommerce 2.6 included important changes for the shipping logic in general. The shipping zones were introduced but also important changes to the shipping methods. We‚Äôve updated the multi-currency component of WooCommerce Multilingual to accommodate these changes but, as it turns out, we still have a few things that we need to fix. In this post, [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Mihai\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4299:\"<p>WooCommerce 2.6 included important changes for the shipping logic in general. The shipping zones were introduced but also important changes to the shipping methods.</p>\n<p>We‚Äôve updated the multi-currency component of WooCommerce Multilingual to accommodate these changes but, as it turns out, we still have a few things that we need to fix.</p>\n<p>In this post, we‚Äôll go through the issues that we know about (and are handling). If you are having other issues, please let us know, so that we can handle everything.</p>\n<h3>1. When using shortcodes in the optional shipping classes costs for the flat rates</h3>\n<p>In this case, the extra cost for the shipping class will not be converted correctly causing the total shipping cost to not be calculated correctly in secondary currencies.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_997315\" style=\"width: 611px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/2016-08-10_1115.png\"><img class=\" wp-image-997315\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/2016-08-10_1115.png\" alt=\"Shortcodes in shipping class costs\" width=\"601\" height=\"454\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/2016-08-10_1115.png 635w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/2016-08-10_1115-150x113.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/2016-08-10_1115-300x227.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 601px) 100vw, 601px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Shortcodes in shipping class costs</p></div>\n<p>This issue affects version 3.8.4 and we‚Äôre fixing it for the following release &#8211; 3.8.5</p>\n<h3>2. Minimum amount requirement for Free Shipping not working in combination with coupons</h3>\n<p>While the ‚Äòminimum order amount‚Äô option works, the other two options that involve using a coupon that enabled free shipping don‚Äôt always work.<br />\nBecause the amount is not converted correctly into a secondary currency when either of those two options is selected. This means that the Free Shipping method could, incorrectly, get enabled for a secondary currency.</p>\n<p>e.g. if the exchange rate is 2x, the minimum required amount is 100 the cart is 75, when you switch to the secondary currency and the amount is 150, because the minimum required was not converted to 200, the Free Shipping gets enabled.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_997350\" style=\"width: 610px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/2016-08-10_1122.png\"><img class=\" wp-image-997350\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/2016-08-10_1122.png\" alt=\"Minimum requirements for Free Shipping\" width=\"600\" height=\"401\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/2016-08-10_1122.png 604w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/2016-08-10_1122-150x100.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/2016-08-10_1122-300x201.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Minimum requirements for Free Shipping</p></div>\n<p>This issue affects version 3.8.4. In WooCommerce Multilingual 3.8.2, the same thing happened with the ‚ÄòA minimum order amount‚Äô option as well.</p>\n<p>We‚Äôre working on fixing both of these problems as quickly as possible and we plan¬†to release a new version next week.</p>\n<p>If you‚Äôre aware of any other situation where shipping costs are not calculated correctly or there are things that you think can be improved, we‚Äôd love to hear from you so we can get on top of that right away.</p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=6gzGAI20aL0:mM3piFDNKVc:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=6gzGAI20aL0:mM3piFDNKVc:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=6gzGAI20aL0:mM3piFDNKVc:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=6gzGAI20aL0:mM3piFDNKVc:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=6gzGAI20aL0:mM3piFDNKVc:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=6gzGAI20aL0:mM3piFDNKVc:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/6gzGAI20aL0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:96:\"https://wpml.org/2016/08/known-issues-related-shipping-cost-woocommerce-multilingual-3-8-4/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:91:\"https://wpml.org/2016/08/known-issues-related-shipping-cost-woocommerce-multilingual-3-8-4/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"hourly\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/r